<div class='mailer__content'>
  <p class='govuk-body'>Dear <%= @user.first_name %>,</p>

  <p class='govuk-body'>Now that you have the necessary CPD under your belt, apply your learning by demonstrating a positive impact on young people in your school and taking an active role in your professional community.</p>

  <p class='govuk-body'>You might have already engaged and completed some of the activities required to achieve your Teach secondary computing certificate. Remember to tick them off by submitting evidence on your dashboard.</p> 
   

  <p class="govuk-body">
    <%= link_to "Check your dashboard", secondary_certificate_url, class: "govuk-button button" %>
  </p>
  
  <p class='govuk-body'><strong>Need more support?</strong></p>

  <p class='govuk-body'>Your local <%= link_to 'Computing Hub', hubs_url, class: 'ncce-link' %> is there to support you at every step of your professional development journey.</p>
</div>
